<title>UK: Ex-dividends to take 2.408 points off FTSE,June 16.</title>
<headline>Ex-dividends to take 2.408 points off FTSE,June 16.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following FTSE-100 stocks will go ex-dividend on Monday and analysts estimate this will take 2.408 points off the index at the start of trading on June 16.</p>
<p>				 DIVIDEND    INDEX</p>
<p>				 (PENCE)     EFFECT</p>
<p>   COMPANY		    Net   Gross    Gross</p>
<p> * BAA			  7.90   9.875    0.562</p>
<p> * Boots		     14.30  17.875    0.947</p>
<p> * Severn Trent	    26.00  32.500    0.650</p>
<p> * 3i			   5.70   7.125    0.249</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 7717</p>
